summary: AN ORDINANCE approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 6535 for the improvement of The ALLEY in BLOCK 13, REPLAT OF BLOCKS 1, 2, 6, 7, 13, 14 and 23, NORTH SEATTLE, being the alley between 3rd Avenue West and 2nd Avenue West from West Republican street to West Mercer Street; by paving and otherwise improving the same.
